description: Now these text faces are flipping small tables that look like ┫, ┻, ┠ or ┳. It really depends on what angle in flight the tables are. You can combine all three small tables to show the table is actually flipping over in the air. This is a great way to add motion into your emoticon, which takes it to the next level.
